Class ICD11DiagnosesSystem

java.lang.Object
com.clinexa.basediagnosis.systems.ICD11DiagnosesSystem
All Implemented Interfaces:
DiagnosesSystem
public final class ICD11DiagnosesSystem extends Object implements DiagnosesSystem
ICD 11-based symptoms and diagnoses management system.
Can be used to get subcategories of ICD 11, their subcategories, diagnoses and symptoms in them, get information by ICD 11 code etc.
Since:
0.1-dev.1
Author:
Nikita S.
